The mathematical concepts, definitions, theorems, proofs, and
algorithms introduced in this repository — including but not
limited to the palette-expansion number p(G), the identity
χ(G) = 1 + p(G), Construction 8.1, Lemma 8.3f, and the
Anti-Destruction Theorem — are the original intellectual
contribution of Mizael Antonio Tovar Reyes.

Any use, citation, or reference to these mathematical results
must clearly credit:

  Mizael Antonio Tovar Reyes
  "Palette-Expansion Numbers and a Constructive Proof of
  Hadwiger's Conjecture," Version 20, March 2026.

